<sect1 id="TRUNCATE">
  <!-- DNT-Start --><title>TRUNCATE</title><!-- DNT-End -->

  <para><emphasis role="bold"><!-- DNT-Start -->TRUNCATE<!-- DNT-End --><indexterm>
      <primary><!-- DNT-Start -->TRUNCATE<!-- DNT-End --></primary>
    </indexterm>(</emphasis><emphasis>real_value</emphasis><emphasis
  role="bold">)</emphasis></para>

  <para><informaltable colsep="1" frame="all" rowsep="1">
      <tgroup cols="2">
        <colspec colwidth="79.10pt" />

        <colspec colwidth="273.70pt" />

        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry><!-- DNT-Start --><emphasis>real_value</emphasis><!-- DNT-End --></entry>

            <entry>The floating-point value to truncate.</entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry><!-- DNT-Start -->Return:<!-- DNT-End --></entry>

            <entry><!-- DNT-Start -->TRUNCATE<!-- DNT-End --> returns a single integer value.</entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
    </informaltable></para>

  <para>The <emphasis role="bold"><!-- DNT-Start -->TRUNCATE<!-- DNT-End --> </emphasis>function<indexterm>
      <primary><!-- DNT-Start -->TRUNCATE<!-- DNT-End --> Function</primary>
    </indexterm> returns the integer portion of the
  <emphasis>real_value</emphasis>.</para>

  <para>Example:</para>

  <!-- DNT-Start --><programlisting>SomeRealValue := 3.75;
INTEGER4 MyVal := TRUNCATE(SomeRealValue); // MyVal is 3
</programlisting><!-- DNT-End -->

  <para>See Also: <link linkend="ROUND"><!-- DNT-Start -->ROUND<!-- DNT-End --></link>, <link linkend="ROUNDUP"><!-- DNT-Start -->ROUNDUP<!-- DNT-End --></link></para>
</sect1>
